Detailed Description

Provdes dummy input signals which can be used by the robot.

Author
Robert Mitchell

Designed for testing purposes. Cues can be synthesised with a magnitude, direction, and "sensitivity". This node is designed to be simple and general, we can have any number of them running on the network at any time (so long as they are uniquely named).
